  "prompt": "What is a teacher?",
  "response": "A teacher is an individual who facilitates learning by imparting knowledge, skills, and values to students. They play a crucial role in education systems by designing and delivering instructional materials, assessing student progress, and fostering an environment that encourages intellectual and personal growth. Teachers often specialize in specific subjects or age groups and use various pedagogical strategies to engage students and accommodate diverse learning styles. Beyond academic instruction, teachers also serve as mentors and role models, helping to guide students in their social and emotional development.",
